Privacy Policy for Math Mastermind:

At Math Mastermind, we value the privacy of our users and are committed to protecting their personal information. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard the information provided by users while using our mobile application.

Information Collection and Use:
We do not collect any personally identifiable information (PII) from users of Math Mastermind. The app does not require any registration or login, and we do not collect names, email addresses, or other personal details.

Non-Personal Information:
Math Mastermind may collect non-personal information such as device information (e.g., device type, operating system, and version), usage statistics, and analytics data. This information is used solely for the purpose of improving the app's functionality and enhancing the user experience.

Third-Party Services:
Math Mastermind may integrate third-party services such as analytics tools, ad networks, and crash reporting services. These services may collect non-personal information as described in their respective privacy policies. We encourage users to review the privacy policies of these third-party services.

Advertising:
Math Mastermind may display advertisements from third-party ad networks. These ad networks may use cookies and similar technologies to collect non-personal information for targeted advertising purposes. Users can opt out of personalized ads by adjusting their device settings or by following the instructions provided by the ad network.

Children's Privacy:
Math Mastermind is intended for general audiences and does not knowingly collect personal information from children under the age of 13. If a parent or guardian becomes aware that their child has provided us with personal information, they should contact us, and we will promptly delete the information from our records.

Data Security:
We take reasonable precautions to protect the information collected by Math Mastermind. However, no method of transmission over the internet or electronic storage is completely secure. We cannot guarantee the absolute security of users' information, and users provide information at their own risk.

Changes to This Privacy Policy:
We reserve the right to update or modify this Privacy Policy at any time. Users are encouraged to review this policy periodically for any changes. Continued use of Math Mastermind after any modifications to the Privacy Policy constitutes acceptance of the changes.

Contact Us:
If you have any questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy or the practices of Math Mastermind, please contact us at [email address].

This Privacy Policy was last updated on 05-06-2023.
